### Reset source records and vectors
POST http://localhost:8080/api/demo/reset

### Seed ordinary application records
POST http://localhost:8080/api/demo/seed

### No indexed evidence exists yet
GET http://localhost:8080/api/knowledge/search?q=I%20cannot%20sign%20in%20after%20too%20many%20attempts

### Project and index the articles with AI Fabric
POST http://localhost:8080/api/demo/index

### Search by meaning rather than an exact title
GET http://localhost:8080/api/knowledge/search?q=I%20cannot%20sign%20in%20after%20too%20many%20attempts

### Verify source and vector counts separately
GET http://localhost:8080/api/demo/readiness
